1
00:00:00,340 --> 00:00:01,640
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:01,640 --> 00:00:03,410
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,480 --> 00:00:05,210
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:09,850 --> 00:00:11,350
(Episode 48)

5
00:00:14,050 --> 00:00:16,120
Why are we in his office
when he's not even here?

6
00:00:16,860 --> 00:00:20,430
Can you imagine how furious
Park Tae Ho must be right now?

7
00:00:20,690 --> 00:00:23,030
And on top of that,
I have to bring up Temi Bio.

8
00:00:23,430 --> 00:00:25,100
It's too risky
to go in empty-handed.

9
00:00:25,660 --> 00:00:29,230
This is exactly
when we need hard evidence.

10
00:00:29,300 --> 00:00:33,000
But you can't
just tear the place apart like this!

11
00:00:34,570 --> 00:00:35,710
I have to find...

12
00:00:37,180 --> 00:00:38,840
hard evidence.

13
00:00:39,940 --> 00:00:42,210
(Temi Bio Corporate Review,
M and A Review Material)

14
00:00:44,320 --> 00:00:45,750
That brat Park Min Jun...

15
00:00:45,820 --> 00:00:47,620
has been digging into
what happened seven years ago.

16
00:00:48,150 --> 00:00:49,150
What?

17
00:00:50,290 --> 00:00:52,320
(Chairman Park Tae Ho)

18
00:00:52,390 --> 00:00:56,190
Ms. Choi's mother said he showed up
at her house asking questions.

19
00:00:56,560 --> 00:00:58,100
He was asking
about the Temi Bio merger...

20
00:00:58,500 --> 00:01:00,470
and the car accident.

21
00:01:01,200 --> 00:01:02,300
I knew it.

22
00:01:03,300 --> 00:01:05,200
So it is about
what happened seven years ago.

23
00:01:06,470 --> 00:01:08,910
You said that brat argued with you
and then left home.

24
00:01:09,540 --> 00:01:11,280
He must've found something out.

25
00:01:12,140 --> 00:01:15,310
And that witch Kim Myung Hui
might know something too.

26
00:01:16,180 --> 00:01:18,850
Before those two conspire
to expose you,

27
00:01:19,350 --> 00:01:20,390
you need to shut them down.

28
00:01:25,890 --> 00:01:26,890
Sir.

29
00:01:35,300 --> 00:01:36,300
Sir?

30
00:01:36,570 --> 00:01:38,840
These documents are
from Min Jun's office.

31
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:41,640
He was investigating
what happened seven years ago...

32
00:01:42,410 --> 00:01:44,380
involving Temi Bio.

33
00:01:45,410 --> 00:01:46,410
Why?

34
00:01:47,810 --> 00:01:48,850
That's...

35
00:01:49,580 --> 00:01:52,580
Why is he digging up something
that's over and done with?

36
00:01:53,890 --> 00:01:55,420
Does this have something to do...

37
00:01:55,550 --> 00:01:56,920
with him throwing a fit...

38
00:01:57,190 --> 00:01:59,760
and saying he doesn't want
to be my son anymore?

39
00:02:01,860 --> 00:02:03,560
What did Min Jun find out?

40
00:02:03,560 --> 00:02:05,060
And what do you know?

41
00:02:06,870 --> 00:02:08,000
Spit it out.

42
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:15,740
I don't know anything about this.

43
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:18,810
How could you possibly not know?

44
00:02:23,310 --> 00:02:25,350
The two of you are inseparable.

45
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:28,290
He wouldn't do something this big
without telling you.

46
00:02:29,790 --> 00:02:32,720
Why is investigating Temi Bio
such a big deal?

47
00:02:33,660 --> 00:02:35,560
Just because Min Jun left home,

48
00:02:36,030 --> 00:02:37,930
don't you dare try
to frame him like this.

49
00:02:38,860 --> 00:02:41,430
- They're not strange accusations.
- Sir,

50
00:02:42,300 --> 00:02:44,440
Min Jun is in charge
of the bio division.

51
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:47,940
He was only gathering data
and doing research for his job.

52
00:02:48,740 --> 00:02:53,140
Why would you think he left home
because of Temi Bio?

53
00:02:58,020 --> 00:03:00,020
Look at her,
pretending she knows nothing.

54
00:03:01,090 --> 00:03:04,320
As if you could ever prove
I know anything.

55
00:03:08,930 --> 00:03:10,360
Regarding the Temi Bio issue,

56
00:03:11,830 --> 00:03:14,000
I'm angry that he went against me.

57
00:03:14,500 --> 00:03:17,240
I told him not to dredge up
the unpleasant past,

58
00:03:17,500 --> 00:03:18,740
but he wouldn't listen.

59
00:03:20,370 --> 00:03:21,370
I see.

60
00:03:22,310 --> 00:03:25,440
If you were offended,
I apologize on his behalf.

61
00:03:25,980 --> 00:03:29,710
When Min Jun comes back,
I'll be sure to relay your wishes.

62
00:03:29,910 --> 00:03:30,920
So?

63
00:03:32,180 --> 00:03:33,650
Where is Min Jun now?

64
00:03:36,420 --> 00:03:39,160
I still haven't been able
to reach him.

65
00:03:39,620 --> 00:03:43,090
Find him, no matter what it takes,
and bring him to me.

66
00:03:43,860 --> 00:03:46,930
I'm going to warn him
about Temi Bio myself,

67
00:03:47,600 --> 00:03:50,770
and I'll ask him
why he disrespected me...

68
00:03:51,870 --> 00:03:53,240
and stormed out of the house.

69
00:03:59,580 --> 00:04:02,680
How dare you frame my Min Jun?

70
00:04:03,050 --> 00:04:04,380
Frame him?

71
00:04:05,020 --> 00:04:06,650
I was just telling the truth.

72
00:04:09,050 --> 00:04:12,990
Min Jun knows about the incident
from seven years ago, doesn't he?

73
00:04:15,390 --> 00:04:18,800
Instead of glaring at me,
you should be looking for your kid.

74
00:04:19,700 --> 00:04:23,600
Not that he'd come back
even if you did find him.

75
00:04:42,190 --> 00:04:44,620
(Division 1 Director's Office)

76
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:53,530
A report came in
from the bio research institute.

77
00:04:54,270 --> 00:04:56,470
There are a few things
that need his approval,

78
00:04:56,770 --> 00:04:58,040
but it seems he didn't come in
to work today.

79
00:05:00,270 --> 00:05:03,140
I hope nothing's wrong at home.

80
00:05:04,540 --> 00:05:06,740
Is there something going on
between you two?

81
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:12,680
It's always like this
whenever Park Min Jun comes up.

82
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:14,920
Forget it.

83
00:05:15,490 --> 00:05:16,490
Park Min Jun.

84
00:05:19,520 --> 00:05:21,430
He argued with our father
and left home.

85
00:05:21,830 --> 00:05:23,390
What? Why?

86
00:05:24,760 --> 00:05:26,400
What was the argument about?

87
00:05:27,400 --> 00:05:28,830
I don't know the specifics.

88
00:05:29,770 --> 00:05:32,000
He suddenly announced he was
cutting ties with our father...

89
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:33,840
and stormed out.

90
00:05:35,670 --> 00:05:37,140
That's why I'm telling you.

91
00:05:37,340 --> 00:05:38,340
I was hoping...

92
00:05:39,410 --> 00:05:41,050
you knew something about it.

93
00:05:44,150 --> 00:05:45,980
Even his own family doesn't know,

94
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:48,090
so how would I?

95
00:05:52,820 --> 00:05:54,590
Park Min Jun.
He's in his office, right?

96
00:05:55,290 --> 00:05:56,290
No.

97
00:05:56,690 --> 00:05:57,730
No?

98
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:08,740
- Then where is he?
- None of your business.

99
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:16,050
Can we talk...

100
00:06:16,810 --> 00:06:18,120
for a moment?

101
00:06:29,890 --> 00:06:30,930
Make it quick.

102
00:06:31,260 --> 00:06:33,300
I have to find Park Min Jun
and talk to him.

103
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:36,370
Why are you so desperate
to find Park Min Jun?

104
00:06:36,700 --> 00:06:39,700
Is your plan
to blackmail the chairman failing?

105
00:06:40,610 --> 00:06:43,910
Or is Park Min Jun
getting in your way?

106
00:06:44,140 --> 00:06:45,610
That's none of your business.

107
00:06:48,010 --> 00:06:49,150
Please tell me...

108
00:06:49,980 --> 00:06:51,550
you didn't get caught.

109
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:53,920
What?

110
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:56,720
With blackmail,

111
00:06:57,160 --> 00:07:00,790
the key to the negotiation
is the battle of wills.

112
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:05,160
The last thing you want...

113
00:07:07,530 --> 00:07:09,830
is for them to see you
looking that anxious.

114
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:13,240
No matter how much
Chairman Park pressures you,

115
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:15,440
you have to push back even harder.

116
00:07:17,580 --> 00:07:19,240
If you show any sign of weakness,

117
00:07:19,880 --> 00:07:24,020
you really might get eaten alive.

118
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:29,920
Of course,

119
00:07:30,520 --> 00:07:34,430
if you're scared and want to quit,
I can't stop you.

120
00:07:38,930 --> 00:07:40,400
Do you think...

121
00:07:40,670 --> 00:07:42,930
I'm still intimidated
by Chairman Park?

122
00:07:44,170 --> 00:07:46,600
The more he pushes,
the harder I'll push back...

123
00:07:47,510 --> 00:07:49,970
until I get everything I want.

124
00:07:52,380 --> 00:07:53,380
Just you watch.

125
00:08:03,750 --> 00:08:04,920
That's right, Choi Yu Na.

126
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:07,930
Keep pushing back
against Chairman Park.

127
00:08:08,990 --> 00:08:13,160
The uglier the fight gets,
the sooner it'll all be over.

128
00:08:15,070 --> 00:08:16,100
Because...

129
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,670
I want to end all of this...

130
00:08:19,500 --> 00:08:20,910
before Min Jun comes back.

131
00:08:46,100 --> 00:08:48,330
Did you call me here
about Director Park Min Jun?

132
00:08:49,330 --> 00:08:50,500
How did you know?

133
00:08:50,970 --> 00:08:52,970
Director Park Hyun Jun told me...

134
00:08:53,370 --> 00:08:55,870
that he argued with the chairman
and left home.

135
00:08:56,640 --> 00:08:59,940
Have you heard from Min Jun at all?

136
00:09:00,580 --> 00:09:03,580
If you have any idea where he is,
please tell me.

137
00:09:05,650 --> 00:09:09,150
I'm not sure.
We don't really keep in touch.

138
00:09:12,390 --> 00:09:13,990
Right. Of course.

139
00:09:15,490 --> 00:09:17,560
I asked impulsively
because I was worried.

140
00:09:18,230 --> 00:09:21,130
If you happen to hear from Min Jun,
please let me know.

141
00:09:21,730 --> 00:09:22,730
I will.

142
00:09:25,900 --> 00:09:26,900
This is just a thought,

143
00:09:29,510 --> 00:09:34,050
but when Director Park comes back,
how about assigning him overseas?

144
00:09:34,810 --> 00:09:35,810
Excuse me?

145
00:09:37,110 --> 00:09:38,750
I don't know what happened,

146
00:09:38,980 --> 00:09:40,750
but if his argument
with the chairman...

147
00:09:40,750 --> 00:09:41,920
made him leave home,

148
00:09:42,020 --> 00:09:43,920
some distance between them
might be good.

149
00:09:45,090 --> 00:09:47,460
With time,
it could all be forgotten...

150
00:09:48,730 --> 00:09:49,790
and become...

151
00:09:50,730 --> 00:09:52,500
a thing of the past.

152
00:09:53,730 --> 00:09:55,170
I'll be the one to handle that.

153
00:09:55,330 --> 00:09:58,400
I appreciate the concern,
but you may leave now.

154
00:10:10,750 --> 00:10:12,620
Become a thing of the past?

155
00:10:21,090 --> 00:10:23,760
Hey, what are you still doing here?

156
00:10:23,830 --> 00:10:25,900
I told you to go find
Min Jun already.

157
00:10:25,930 --> 00:10:29,300
I'd love to get out there,
but the part-timer still isn't here.

158
00:10:32,340 --> 00:10:33,340
Na Yeon,

159
00:10:33,500 --> 00:10:36,740
you're only getting here now?
You're 30 minutes late.

160
00:10:36,810 --> 00:10:38,080
What was that?

161
00:10:38,210 --> 00:10:40,110
I said you were 30 minutes late.

162
00:10:40,180 --> 00:10:41,510
Am I?

163
00:10:42,050 --> 00:10:44,150
Then just dock my pay.

164
00:10:44,250 --> 00:10:45,280
What?

165
00:10:50,920 --> 00:10:51,920
Hey.

166
00:10:52,260 --> 00:10:53,990
Where on earth did you find
this part-timer?

167
00:10:54,890 --> 00:10:59,500
She's not very punctual,
but she's a hard worker.

168
00:10:59,730 --> 00:11:03,370
You're such a pushover.
Unbelievable.

169
00:11:05,170 --> 00:11:06,440
What brings you here?

170
00:11:07,040 --> 00:11:10,540
I have to leave right now.
I think I know where Min Jun is.

171
00:11:10,940 --> 00:11:12,480
- Where is he?
- Where?

172
00:11:26,620 --> 00:11:28,760
(The late Baek Jun Gi,
The late Baek Jin Ju)

173
00:11:41,640 --> 00:11:42,770
I'm sorry.

174
00:11:44,540 --> 00:11:46,540
Seven years ago, I...

175
00:11:47,850 --> 00:11:49,580
I was so foolish.

176
00:11:51,080 --> 00:11:53,580
You're the father Jin Ju loved
with all her heart.

177
00:11:54,050 --> 00:11:55,120
For a man like that...

178
00:11:55,990 --> 00:11:58,390
to commit a crime
and even take Jin Ju's life?

179
00:12:02,190 --> 00:12:03,730
It shouldn't have made any sense.

180
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:09,070
Overwhelmed by the grief
of losing Jin Ju,

181
00:12:09,470 --> 00:12:12,200
all I did was blindly hate
and resent you.

182
00:12:15,810 --> 00:12:17,410
Please forgive me...

183
00:12:20,340 --> 00:12:21,650
for the way I acted.

184
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:35,390
As Park Tae Ho's son,

185
00:12:36,030 --> 00:12:38,530
I know I don't deserve her,

186
00:12:39,400 --> 00:12:41,470
but I'm still in love with Jin Ju.

187
00:12:42,070 --> 00:12:43,070
For that,

188
00:12:44,640 --> 00:12:45,940
I'm truly sorry.

189
00:13:02,220 --> 00:13:03,350
I had a feeling...

190
00:13:03,820 --> 00:13:05,390
you'd be here.

191
00:13:06,560 --> 00:13:08,190
How did you know?

192
00:13:08,690 --> 00:13:10,390
I knew about it.

193
00:13:12,430 --> 00:13:13,430
What?

194
00:13:17,230 --> 00:13:18,270
Kim Myung Hui.

195
00:13:19,170 --> 00:13:21,770
She got what was coming to her
for using my Hyun Jun like that.

196
00:13:22,410 --> 00:13:25,780
I've been fuming for days.
It's such a relief.

197
00:13:26,110 --> 00:13:28,850
Do you really think
Park Min Jun knows everything...

198
00:13:28,850 --> 00:13:30,210
from seven years ago?

199
00:13:30,280 --> 00:13:31,680
What happened seven years ago?

200
00:13:36,420 --> 00:13:40,320
Are you saying that incident
is why Min Jun left home?

201
00:13:41,460 --> 00:13:42,860
Is that incident
from seven years ago...

202
00:13:43,690 --> 00:13:44,900
related to Temi Bio?

203
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:46,000
What?

204
00:13:47,100 --> 00:13:49,270
Well, that's...

205
00:13:51,740 --> 00:13:52,740
Park Hyun Jun.

206
00:13:53,470 --> 00:13:55,870
We can't let this chance slip away.

207
00:13:56,970 --> 00:13:59,780
Now that Park Min Jun stormed out
after confronting your father,

208
00:14:00,140 --> 00:14:03,180
you need to secure your place
as Adele's successor.

209
00:14:04,180 --> 00:14:07,150
Don't you dare mention Temi Bio
from seven years ago.

210
00:14:07,690 --> 00:14:08,690
Got it?

211
00:14:08,920 --> 00:14:11,790
So, it is about Temi Bio then?

212
00:14:12,260 --> 00:14:15,160
If it drove Park Min Jun
to argue with Father and leave,

213
00:14:16,590 --> 00:14:18,530
then Father must've been at fault.

214
00:14:20,430 --> 00:14:22,700
That's hardly the only wrong thing
your father has done.

215
00:14:23,230 --> 00:14:25,900
Things like this happen in business.

216
00:14:27,140 --> 00:14:29,210
Stop playing detective over nothing.

217
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:31,480
Just focus on becoming Adele's heir,

218
00:14:32,180 --> 00:14:33,180
or better yet,

219
00:14:33,440 --> 00:14:35,210
think about the marriage you want.

220
00:14:36,650 --> 00:14:37,880
That's the safer bet.

221
00:14:38,520 --> 00:14:39,550
All right?

222
00:14:40,520 --> 00:14:43,220
I'm being very serious this time.

223
00:14:50,930 --> 00:14:52,000
Mr. Song,

224
00:14:52,860 --> 00:14:54,160
you seem to know all about it.

225
00:14:55,100 --> 00:14:57,030
Come on, what is it? Spit it out.

226
00:14:57,330 --> 00:14:58,340
Well...

227
00:15:01,240 --> 00:15:04,810
Just because Park Min Jun knows
doesn't mean you have to.

228
00:15:05,240 --> 00:15:07,080
Park Min Jun is his own person,

229
00:15:07,580 --> 00:15:10,080
and you're yours. Right?

230
00:15:10,910 --> 00:15:12,020
You just...

231
00:15:12,850 --> 00:15:15,250
Right, that's it. Go your own way.

232
00:15:17,490 --> 00:15:20,160
Just focus on yourself. Okay?

233
00:15:29,570 --> 00:15:32,170
Back during the Temi Bio incident
seven years ago,

234
00:15:32,970 --> 00:15:34,910
my father did something wrong.

235
00:15:35,740 --> 00:15:37,640
But what exactly did he do?

236
00:15:38,740 --> 00:15:40,240
Do I have to find that out too?

237
00:15:43,650 --> 00:15:45,150
Am I even supposed to know?

238
00:15:52,720 --> 00:15:54,790
So you knew everything all along?

239
00:15:55,090 --> 00:15:56,090
Yes.

240
00:15:58,760 --> 00:16:00,230
These two people here...

241
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:04,030
lost their lives unjustly
because of Chairman Park.

242
00:16:05,840 --> 00:16:07,140
I knew that.

243
00:16:09,410 --> 00:16:10,910
If you knew, why didn't you...

244
00:16:10,910 --> 00:16:14,140
I was worried you'd be hurt.

245
00:16:15,710 --> 00:16:17,250
Besides, you'd be in danger...

246
00:16:17,250 --> 00:16:18,980
Don't tell me
it was because of Adele.

247
00:16:20,080 --> 00:16:22,720
Were you so afraid
of having to give up Adele...

248
00:16:23,520 --> 00:16:24,860
that you chose to ignore the truth?

249
00:16:28,330 --> 00:16:29,330
Yes.

250
00:16:30,690 --> 00:16:32,560
I'd be lying if I said no.

251
00:16:32,560 --> 00:16:33,600
Mother.

252
00:16:33,600 --> 00:16:36,630
I want the power of Adele
that Chairman Park has.

253
00:16:36,970 --> 00:16:39,570
It's the only way to gain the power
to bring the truth to light...

254
00:16:39,570 --> 00:16:42,070
and do what's right,
even if it takes time.

255
00:16:44,380 --> 00:16:46,680
Even if it meant living...

256
00:16:47,380 --> 00:16:49,150
alongside a murderer,

257
00:16:50,810 --> 00:16:53,020
I couldn't give up on Adele.

258
00:16:57,290 --> 00:16:58,290
But...

259
00:17:01,390 --> 00:17:03,130
it'll be different for you.

260
00:17:05,030 --> 00:17:07,060
You've lost someone you love,

261
00:17:08,670 --> 00:17:09,970
so the pain...

262
00:17:11,030 --> 00:17:12,670
must be so much greater.

263
00:17:17,780 --> 00:17:19,210
If the pain is too much...

264
00:17:20,080 --> 00:17:21,510
and you need to walk away,

265
00:17:24,980 --> 00:17:26,880
I won't force you this time.

266
00:17:29,320 --> 00:17:30,320
Do you mean that?

267
00:17:30,620 --> 00:17:31,620
Yes.

268
00:17:32,720 --> 00:17:35,560
From this point on,
it has to be your choice alone.

269
00:17:36,360 --> 00:17:38,800
You don't have to factor my worries
into your decision.

270
00:17:39,000 --> 00:17:43,400
If you leave, don't look back
and don't worry about me. Just go.

271
00:17:46,070 --> 00:17:47,070
But...

272
00:17:48,570 --> 00:17:50,470
if you can't let it go,

273
00:17:52,310 --> 00:17:53,680
and there's something you must do,

274
00:17:53,680 --> 00:17:55,080
even if it means
fighting your father,

275
00:17:56,050 --> 00:17:57,110
then come back.

276
00:17:59,580 --> 00:18:01,350
If you come back ready to fight,

277
00:18:03,750 --> 00:18:04,790
I'll...

278
00:18:05,520 --> 00:18:06,760
help you.

279
00:18:32,080 --> 00:18:34,150
(The late Baek Jun Gi,
The late Baek Jin Ju)

280
00:18:42,330 --> 00:18:43,330
Dan Hui.

281
00:18:43,890 --> 00:18:45,500
Here, have some warm tea.

282
00:18:46,260 --> 00:18:47,260
Thank you.

283
00:18:50,470 --> 00:18:54,770
Hey, forget the tea.
Go get dinner started.

284
00:18:54,940 --> 00:18:57,510
She's been too worried about Min Jun
to eat all day.

285
00:18:57,710 --> 00:18:59,310
We should get her something to eat.

286
00:18:59,480 --> 00:19:01,450
Oh, you're right.

287
00:19:01,650 --> 00:19:03,650
Give me a second.
I'll go prepare it now.

288
00:19:03,650 --> 00:19:05,780
No, it's okay.

289
00:19:06,120 --> 00:19:09,420
What do you mean you're okay?
Eat something before you pass out.

290
00:19:10,220 --> 00:19:12,690
She's right.
You don't look well as it is.

291
00:19:12,920 --> 00:19:15,990
I'll make abalone porridge,
so please eat some before you go.

292
00:19:20,760 --> 00:19:22,400
Try not to worry too much.

293
00:19:22,800 --> 00:19:26,540
Whether he runs or fights,
I'm sure he'll decide for himself.

294
00:19:27,340 --> 00:19:29,570
Of course. He will, right?

295
00:19:30,740 --> 00:19:33,140
Are you really okay, though?

296
00:19:35,650 --> 00:19:37,750
What are you going to do
if Min Jun doesn't come back?

297
00:19:38,420 --> 00:19:41,690
I'll have to find a way,
no matter what.

298
00:19:43,120 --> 00:19:47,890
A way to take Adele from Oh Jung Ran
without Min Jun.

299
00:19:49,330 --> 00:19:51,660
Do you have a plan in mind?

300
00:19:53,130 --> 00:19:56,230
I think I may need
to be a bit ruthless.

301
00:19:57,070 --> 00:19:58,300
Would that be okay?

302
00:19:58,370 --> 00:20:01,540
Of course.
With Oh Jung Ran running wild,

303
00:20:01,610 --> 00:20:03,170
we can't just sit back and take it.

304
00:20:09,250 --> 00:20:12,750
Given the circumstances,
it's safe to assume...

305
00:20:13,350 --> 00:20:15,520
he knows everything about
what happened seven years ago.

306
00:20:16,090 --> 00:20:18,420
That must be why
he caused such a scene...

307
00:20:19,520 --> 00:20:21,330
and threatened to cut ties with me.

308
00:20:23,060 --> 00:20:25,730
I need to find out where
and how he learned the truth...

309
00:20:26,760 --> 00:20:29,230
before I can figure out
how to clean this mess up.

310
00:20:39,180 --> 00:20:40,740
Chloe, what brings you here?

311
00:20:41,140 --> 00:20:43,250
It's about Director Park Min Jun.
Actually,

312
00:20:43,510 --> 00:20:46,550
I'm here to talk to you
about Ms. Choi Yu Na.

313
00:20:47,520 --> 00:20:51,190
I heard you went to the police station
to help Ms. Choi.

314
00:20:51,720 --> 00:20:53,220
If this is about that,

315
00:20:54,260 --> 00:20:56,430
you don't need to explain.

316
00:20:56,430 --> 00:21:00,060
Ms. Choi threatened you, didn't she?

317
00:21:05,470 --> 00:21:06,470
It's me.

318
00:21:07,040 --> 00:21:09,570
I've got something we can use
to pressure Chairman Park.

319
00:21:11,310 --> 00:21:12,640
It's the truth about...

320
00:21:12,640 --> 00:21:14,610
what happened seven years ago
that he's been hiding.

321
00:21:16,610 --> 00:21:19,550
What truth?
What happened seven years ago?

322
00:21:19,920 --> 00:21:21,490
A secret that Park Min Jun,

323
00:21:21,820 --> 00:21:23,920
of all people, must never find out.

324
00:21:26,190 --> 00:21:28,430
I knew it. You did know something.

325
00:21:29,230 --> 00:21:30,230
Tell me.

326
00:21:30,860 --> 00:21:33,660
What happened seven years ago
that I'm not supposed to know about?

327
00:21:35,930 --> 00:21:37,400
Tell me right now.

328
00:21:42,910 --> 00:21:45,280
Quite an interesting call, isn't it?

329
00:21:48,110 --> 00:21:49,410
Why are you...

330
00:21:50,110 --> 00:21:52,020
telling me this?

331
00:21:53,680 --> 00:21:56,120
Because I want out.

332
00:21:56,520 --> 00:21:57,890
You want out?

333
00:21:58,260 --> 00:22:02,690
I told the police what I knew
because I didn't want to lie,

334
00:22:02,930 --> 00:22:06,030
but Ms. Choi seems to think
I was helping her.

335
00:22:07,160 --> 00:22:09,370
She keeps bothering me,

336
00:22:09,570 --> 00:22:12,440
asking me
to help her get revenge on you.

337
00:22:12,700 --> 00:22:14,770
I told her I'm not interested,
but she keeps calling...

338
00:22:14,970 --> 00:22:16,640
to change my mind.

339
00:22:17,440 --> 00:22:18,640
And that's how...

340
00:22:19,140 --> 00:22:22,210
she ended up saying strange things
to Park Min Jun.

341
00:22:23,080 --> 00:22:24,310
And another thing.

342
00:22:25,420 --> 00:22:27,580
This truth about the incident
from seven years ago.

343
00:22:30,990 --> 00:22:32,320
Even if there's something to it,

344
00:22:33,890 --> 00:22:37,130
that has nothing to do with me.

345
00:22:38,730 --> 00:22:41,200
I don't want to get caught up...

346
00:22:41,200 --> 00:22:43,470
in a complicated situation
because of Ms. Choi.

347
00:22:45,000 --> 00:22:48,570
Wouldn't it be best for both of us
if you took care of it?

348
00:22:49,670 --> 00:22:50,670
All right.

349
00:22:51,440 --> 00:22:54,850
I'll take it from here.

350
00:22:56,110 --> 00:22:59,750
I'm glad to hear that.
Then I'll leave it in your hands.

351
00:23:07,690 --> 00:23:10,860
So the one
who got Min Jun worked up...

352
00:23:11,330 --> 00:23:13,360
was Choi Yu Na, that piece of work?

353
00:23:14,200 --> 00:23:16,600
And after all that,
she dared to stand before me,

354
00:23:17,100 --> 00:23:18,440
threaten me,

355
00:23:19,200 --> 00:23:20,970
and demand compensation?

356
00:23:23,410 --> 00:23:25,410
Oh my, what in the world?

357
00:23:28,550 --> 00:23:31,520
Goodness, what's all this? My gosh.

358
00:23:33,220 --> 00:23:35,450
What is this? Goodness me.

359
00:23:36,750 --> 00:23:39,420
Chairman Park, what brings you here?

360
00:23:39,690 --> 00:23:44,160
Whatever this is, you should
probably take your shoes off first.

361
00:23:44,230 --> 00:23:45,760
We're not in the US, you know.

362
00:23:47,300 --> 00:23:49,270
I'm pretty sure Ms. Choi knows...

363
00:23:50,470 --> 00:23:52,040
why...

364
00:23:53,900 --> 00:23:55,170
I'm doing this.

365
00:23:55,970 --> 00:23:56,970
What?

366
00:23:58,040 --> 00:23:59,040
What...

367
00:23:59,310 --> 00:24:02,480
I have no idea
what you're talking about.

368
00:24:06,820 --> 00:24:07,820
Is that right?

369
00:24:09,820 --> 00:24:11,220
What now?

370
00:24:13,920 --> 00:24:15,130
My goodness!

371
00:24:16,660 --> 00:24:18,560
What do you think you're doing?

372
00:24:18,900 --> 00:24:22,600
What are you doing? Goodness.
Oh, my word.

373
00:24:22,830 --> 00:24:24,530
Manager Kang.

374
00:24:25,370 --> 00:24:26,370
My gosh.

375
00:24:26,970 --> 00:24:30,370
- Goodness, what are you doing?
- Mom! Dad!

376
00:24:30,370 --> 00:24:33,040
Yu Na!

377
00:24:33,310 --> 00:24:35,550
What are you doing to my Yu Na?

378
00:24:35,550 --> 00:24:37,780
For crying out loud. Let go of me!

379
00:24:39,280 --> 00:24:40,450
I'll ask you again.

380
00:24:41,690 --> 00:24:43,220
Do you still not get...

381
00:24:44,290 --> 00:24:45,460
why I'm doing this?

382
00:24:49,030 --> 00:24:51,430
No matter how much
Chairman Park pressures you,

383
00:24:51,460 --> 00:24:53,500
you have to push back even harder.

384
00:24:56,770 --> 00:24:59,300
This must be about Min Jun,

385
00:25:00,440 --> 00:25:02,770
but I didn't tell him a thing.

386
00:25:02,770 --> 00:25:04,110
Still lying, are you?

387
00:25:05,480 --> 00:25:08,280
You won't even beg for forgiveness
or for your life?

388
00:25:08,980 --> 00:25:11,410
I'm telling you,
I didn't say a word!

389
00:25:13,750 --> 00:25:15,850
My own son disrespected me...

390
00:25:16,290 --> 00:25:19,520
and left home,
saying he was cutting ties with me.

391
00:25:21,020 --> 00:25:22,030
What?

392
00:25:23,160 --> 00:25:25,660
Min Jun ran away from home?

393
00:25:33,000 --> 00:25:36,270
He must've found out
what happened seven years ago.

394
00:25:37,210 --> 00:25:40,310
If you're the one
who told him what happened,

395
00:25:40,780 --> 00:25:41,910
kept it from me,

396
00:25:42,250 --> 00:25:44,680
and then had the nerve to threaten me
and demand compensation,

397
00:25:48,250 --> 00:25:49,550
I'll make sure
that mouth of yours...

398
00:25:51,350 --> 00:25:53,590
never speaks another word.

399
00:26:08,070 --> 00:26:09,070
What the...

400
00:26:10,570 --> 00:26:12,680
I didn't even get a chance
to use Park Min Jun,

401
00:26:13,680 --> 00:26:15,450
and all I did
was anger Chairman Park?

402
00:26:26,520 --> 00:26:27,520
Choi Yu Na.

403
00:26:29,030 --> 00:26:31,860
You're terrified, aren't you?

404
00:26:33,760 --> 00:26:34,760
Just wait.

405
00:26:35,600 --> 00:26:38,940
You'll be put out
of your misery soon.

406
00:26:54,180 --> 00:26:56,750
You haven't found Min Jun yet,
have you?

407
00:26:57,420 --> 00:26:58,420
No.

408
00:26:59,320 --> 00:27:00,720
You don't know...

409
00:27:01,660 --> 00:27:03,760
why Min Jun left home either,
do you?

410
00:27:05,400 --> 00:27:06,400
I don't.

411
00:27:12,640 --> 00:27:13,640
What's this?

412
00:27:14,140 --> 00:27:17,240
These are the Temi Bio files
Director Park Min Jun had.

413
00:27:18,440 --> 00:27:21,610
You brought back the files
that made the chairman so angry?

414
00:27:21,680 --> 00:27:24,950
Well, I just didn't feel right
throwing away the files...

415
00:27:25,020 --> 00:27:26,650
Director Park put together.

416
00:27:26,950 --> 00:27:29,350
I thought it'd be better for him
to deal with them when he returns.

417
00:27:31,920 --> 00:27:33,360
Are you heading upstairs?

418
00:27:34,390 --> 00:27:37,490
Could you put these
in his room for me?

419
00:27:37,990 --> 00:27:39,930
I have something to discuss
with Secretary Jung.

420
00:27:40,560 --> 00:27:42,470
Sure. I'll take them.

421
00:27:55,950 --> 00:27:58,850
(Temi Bio Corporate Review,
M and A Review Material)

422
00:28:00,880 --> 00:28:02,390
The Temi Bio files.

423
00:28:03,990 --> 00:28:07,220
Min Jun was investigating
what happened seven years ago,

424
00:28:09,490 --> 00:28:11,360
and Father got angry
when he saw this?

425
00:28:20,870 --> 00:28:22,740
(Not a car accident,
but an explosion...)

426
00:28:22,740 --> 00:28:23,970
(ordered by Park Tae Ho?)

427
00:28:26,080 --> 00:28:27,180
What the heck?

428
00:28:33,020 --> 00:28:35,720
Father was behind the car accident
from seven years ago?

429
00:28:38,860 --> 00:28:40,860
So it wasn't an accident,
but a targeted hit?

430
00:29:01,080 --> 00:29:04,010
Did Park Hyun Jun see the note
we left for him?

431
00:29:04,710 --> 00:29:05,720
Yes.

432
00:29:06,580 --> 00:29:09,190
This is to get back at Oh Jung Ran
for what she did,

433
00:29:09,490 --> 00:29:12,560
and it's also a contingency plan
in case Min Jun doesn't come back.

434
00:29:12,590 --> 00:29:14,290
You don't have to think it's cruel.

435
00:29:15,020 --> 00:29:18,190
Why should Min Jun bear that cruelty
all by himself?

436
00:29:19,360 --> 00:29:22,800
Min Jun lost the one he loved
at the hands of his own father.

437
00:29:23,700 --> 00:29:25,540
Even if this shocks Park Hyun Jun,

438
00:29:25,770 --> 00:29:27,800
it's nothing
compared to Min Jun's pain.

439
00:29:29,340 --> 00:29:32,280
What choice will Hyun Jun make?

440
00:29:33,510 --> 00:29:35,450
Even after learning about
all of Chairman Park's crimes,

441
00:29:35,910 --> 00:29:37,350
will he do as Oh Jung Ran wants...

442
00:29:38,310 --> 00:29:40,520
and step up as Adele's heir?

443
00:29:41,680 --> 00:29:42,920
(Temi Bio CEO Baek Jun Gi
and Daughter Dead)

444
00:29:45,290 --> 00:29:46,290
My father...

445
00:29:49,660 --> 00:29:50,930
killed Baek Jin Ju's father?

446
00:29:54,630 --> 00:29:56,270
So that's why Min Jun...

447
00:30:05,710 --> 00:30:08,280
Son, what's with the look
on your face?

448
00:30:08,810 --> 00:30:09,810
Are you sick?

449
00:30:10,610 --> 00:30:11,610
Father.

450
00:30:12,150 --> 00:30:13,180
What?

451
00:30:13,280 --> 00:30:14,380
Father!

452
00:30:15,420 --> 00:30:16,490
Sir!

453
00:30:17,250 --> 00:30:19,490
What's with you?
Why are you calling for him?

454
00:30:29,830 --> 00:30:30,830
What is it?

455
00:30:31,700 --> 00:30:33,200
What's with you now?

456
00:30:34,400 --> 00:30:35,540
Father, have you...

457
00:30:38,740 --> 00:30:40,210
killed someone too?

458
00:30:42,410 --> 00:30:43,580
What?

459
00:30:44,050 --> 00:30:45,080
Park Hyun Jun!

460
00:30:45,950 --> 00:30:48,450
The Temi Bio car accident
from seven years ago.

461
00:30:49,790 --> 00:30:51,890
I'm asking if you were behind it!

462
00:30:52,660 --> 00:30:55,160
Not you too. What is this nonsense?

463
00:30:56,490 --> 00:30:57,490
He's right.

464
00:30:57,690 --> 00:30:59,630
What's gotten into you
all of a sudden?

465
00:31:02,100 --> 00:31:04,470
Did that brat Min Jun feed you
those crazy ideas too?

466
00:31:05,270 --> 00:31:06,370
Or was it...

467
00:31:07,870 --> 00:31:11,340
You put these ideas
into Hyun Jun's head, didn't you?

468
00:31:12,080 --> 00:31:13,080
Father.

469
00:31:18,380 --> 00:31:19,380
Min Jun.

470
00:31:21,250 --> 00:31:22,250
Min Jun.

471
00:31:25,390 --> 00:31:28,090
Park Min Jun, you...

472
00:31:50,010 --> 00:31:51,710
Father, I...

473
00:31:54,380 --> 00:31:55,550
I was wrong.

474
00:32:37,460 --> 00:32:40,400
(Pearl in Red)

475
00:32:40,730 --> 00:32:43,100
What kind of people are you and Dad?

476
00:32:43,100 --> 00:32:44,100
Hyun Jun, please.

477
00:32:44,100 --> 00:32:47,000
What secrets from the past
are you hiding?

478
00:32:47,270 --> 00:32:50,270
I want to take over Adele.

479
00:32:50,770 --> 00:32:53,310
You mean you'll go against
your own father?

480
00:32:53,610 --> 00:32:55,780
I have to right my father's wrongs.

481
00:32:56,010 --> 00:32:58,380
Have someone follow Min Jun.

482
00:32:58,780 --> 00:33:00,920
And as for Choi Yu Na...

483
00:33:01,250 --> 00:33:03,090
It's time I silenced her.

484
00:33:04,220 --> 00:33:06,220
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
